You are working in a Turborepo monorepo. Packages are in packages/*.

ALWAYS:
- Run turbo commands, not package-level commands, for builds
- Check package.json "exports" field before importing from another package
- Create a changeset after modifying a published package
- Run `tsc --noEmit` repo-wide after changing packages/shared/

NEVER:
- Import from forbidden package dependencies (see CLAUDE.md package boundaries)
- Create circular dependencies between packages
- Edit shared types without checking all consumers compile
- Commit without verifying turbo build passes
